criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ≥ 18 years;

          -  Histopathological diagnosis with LGG according to the 2016 World Health Organization
             (WHO) criteria;

          -  Participants received more than 6 years of school education;

          -  Presence of GRE, take levetiracetam less than 1 month; or do not take any medicine and
             receive any treatment;

          -  No history of biopsy, radiotherapy, or chemotherapy.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Contraindications for MRI;

          -  Head motion greater than 3 mm in translation or 3° in rotation;
